author: @glowshowpk
text: Ok lemme say something here. I really like this group, don't get me wrong but I have a feeling that JYP was trying to copy BTS when they did this video. BTS would come out with dance practice videos like this for the ARMY so that they could be cute with each other. Now Twice did the exact same thing. Don't think I'm saying this because I'm an ARMY, I have now become a ONCE too, but this is too much. At least BTS looked natural in these videos and managed to pull it off by trying to make it seem that it was all thought of on-the-spot, but here Twice looks generally uncomfortable and trying too hard to make this video cute and fun, it's all really obvious.
